      <div class="realpost"><div>
        <blockquote class="thequote">House Budget Committee Chairman Paul Ryan has just released a recklessly bold, 73-page, 10-year budget plan,” he wrote. “At 37 footnotes, it might be the most annotated suicide note in history.</blockquote>
        &mdash;<a href="http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2012/08/06/120806fa_fact_lizza?currentPage=all">Paul Ryan’s Influence on the G.O.P.&#160;: The New Yorker</a>
